<HTML><HEAD>
<TITLE>The Great Railway LNG Project Report.</TITLE> 
<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="AutoGen by Bayleaf Software Inc."> 
<META NAME="SUBJECT" CONTENT="Citation #2465"> 
</HEAD> <BODY BGCOLOR="#ffffff">
<BODY>
<H1>The Great Railway LNG Project Report.</H1><HR>

<B>Title: </B>
The Great Railway LNG Project Report.<BR>

<B>Authors: </B>
Reimer, T.J.<BR>

<B>Source: </B>
Dome Petroleum, 10 pp.<BR>

<B>Date: </B>
<P>

<B>Abstract: </B><BR>

This report outlines concepts associated with the conversion of Canadian railways to an alternative fuel, in particular liquefied natural gas.  Economic aspects, safety, choice of fuel, and transport technology are some of the areas covered.  A pilot prog
ram is suggested and cost/benefit figures projected.  Cost savings are also estimated for a full size conversion project
<P>

<B>Keywords: </B>

CONVERSION,LIQUEFIED,LOCOMOTIVE,NATURAL GAS
<BR><B>File Reference: </B>
549<P>

