<H1>Natural gas compostion and the performance of CNG fuelled vehicles.</H1><HR>

<B>Title: </B>
Natural gas compostion and the performance of CNG fuelled vehicles.<BR>

<B>Authors: </B>
<BR>

<B>Source: </B>
Alternative Fuels Directorate, Ministry of Energy, Private Bag, Wellington,  New Zealand.  Technical Bulletin: TB 2007.<BR>

<B>Date: </B>
<P>

<B>Abstract: </B><BR>

This bulletin looks at how vehicle performance is affected by changes in the composition of natural gas.  It also looks at the gas that is now available in New Zealand and gas that may be produced over the next few years
<P>

<B>Keywords: </B>

COMPOSITION,NATURAL GAS,NEW ZEALAND,PERFORMANCE
<BR><B>File Reference: </B>
1637<P>

