<TITLE>Optimization of Propane Engines for Light Duty Vehicles - Phase I.</TITLE> 
<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="AutoGen by Bayleaf Software Inc."> 
<META NAME="SUBJECT" CONTENT="Citation #1896"> 
</HEAD> <BODY BGCOLOR="#ffffff">
