<DOCHDR>
http://www.bcr.bc.ca:80/catf/review/issue_21/cng_3.htm 204.191.240.6 19970221190138 text/html 6040
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 21 Feb 1997 19:01:59 GMT
