<DOCOLDNO>IA006-000056-B016-9</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.bcr.bc.ca:80/catf/review/issue_27/geopg2.htm 204.191.240.6 19970221185449 text/html 6654
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 21 Feb 1997 18:55:08 GMT
