<DOCNO>WT04-B17-102</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA006-000056-B016-57</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.bcr.bc.ca:80/catf/review/issue_25/steppg2.htm 204.191.240.6 19970221185537 text/html 6473
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 21 Feb 1997 18:55:58 GMT
Server: WebSitePro/1.1g (S/N WPO-22E6)
