<DOCOLDNO>IA006-000056-B016-450</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.bcr.bc.ca:80/catf/review/issue_28/cyl_pg4.htm 204.191.240.6 19970221190209 text/html 8229
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 21 Feb 1997 19:02:30 GMT
Server: WebSitePro/1.1g (S/N WPO-22E6)
