</DOCHDR>
<!DOCTYPE HTML"-//IETF//DTD HTML 3.0//EN">
<HTML>

<HEAD>
<TITLE>CATF Review Newletter: Issue No. 22 (July, 1995)</TITLE>
<META NAME="GENERATOR" CONTENT="Internet Assistant for Word 2.0z Beta>
<META NAME="AUTHOR" CONTENT="Andrea Gomory">
<!-- Last Update: 01/10/96 -->
</HEAD>

<BODY BGCOLOR="#FFFFFF" TEXT="#000000" LINK="#FF0000" VLINK="#8080C0" ALINK="#E629A">
<BASEFONT SIZE=3>

<BODY>
<IMG border=0 SRC="../cr_gifs/catf_pg4.gif"><BR>

<!-- begin table--><!-- total=600 -->
<table border=0 width=630 cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0>

<tr>
<td width=150 valign=top rowspan=1>
<IMG border=0 align=top vspace=6 SRC="../cr_gifs/dot_clr.gif"><BR>
<IMG border=0 align=top SRC="../cr_gifs/toc_thin.gif"><BR>
<A HREF="niche.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="22toc_1b.gif"></A><br>
<IMG border=0 align=top SRC="../cr_gifs/toc_thik.gif"><BR>
<A HREF="ballard.htm"<><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="22toc_2.gif"></A><br>
<IMG border=0 align=top SRC="../cr_gifs/toc_thik.gif"><BR>
<A HREF="online.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="22toc_3.gif"></A><br>
<IMG border=0 align=top SRC="../cr_gifs/toc_thik.gif"><BR>
<A HREF="gotran.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="22toc_4.gif"></A><br>
<IMG border=0 align=top SRC="../cr_gifs/toc_thik.gif"><BR>
<A HREF="students.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="22toc_5.gif"></A><br>
<IMG border=0 align=top SRC="../cr_gifs/toc_thik.gif"><BR>
<A HREF="afv.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="22toc_6.gif"></A><br>
<IMG border=0 align=top SRC="../cr_gifs/toc_thik.gif"><BR>
<A HREF="ngv.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="22toc_7.gif"></A><br>
<IMG border=0 align=top SRC="../cr_gifs/toc_thin.gif"><BR>
</td>

<td valign=top colspan=2 width=480>
<IMG border=0 align=top vspace=3 SRC="../cr_gifs/dot_clr.gif"><BR>
<IMG align=top hspace=10 SRC="../cr_gifs/dot_clr.gif">
The pricing of propane varies widely, depending on supply (in some gas producing areas there can be a significant oversupply in winter, so propane is dumped on the auto fuel market as an
alternative to burning it) and taxes (some states and provinces tax it at an effective rate even higher than gasoline; some states don't tax it at all.) Because of the economics and choices in
refining, the supply of auto propane can be very sensitive to price; a greatly increased supply might result from a small increase in price, as petrochemical users move to imported supplies or
to naptha. Much propane is also used as a fuel in refineries; natural gas could be substituted to free up propane for automotive use.<BR>

<IMG border=0 align=top vspace=3 SRC="../cr_gifs/dot_clr.gif"><BR>
<IMG align=top hspace=10 SRC="../cr_gifs/dot_clr.gif">
Compressed Natural Gas: A good clean motor fuel, widely distributed via pipeline throughout the continent, particularly in urban areas. Vehicle conversions not complex, but because of low energy density of the gaseous fuel, tanks take up a lot of space on board the vehicle and the vehicle may still have less than half its gasoline range. Economical; safe, because the installations must be well made to withstand the pressure underwhich CNG is sold or stored. Fuelling installations tend to be more expensive than for most other fuels, because of costs of compressors and high pressure
storage, but transportation costs (by existing pipelines) tend to be less.<BR>

<IMG border=0 align=top vspace=3 SRC="../cr_gifs/dot_clr.gif"><BR>
<IMG align=top hspace=10 SRC="../cr_gifs/dot_clr.gif">
Liquefied Natural Gas: Most of the advantages of compressed natural gas plus much increased energy density at the expense of cryogenic storage both at the fuelling point and on board the vehicle. Liquefaction of pipeline gas takes considerable energy from the gaseous state.<BR>

<IMG border=0 align=top vspace=3 SRC="../cr_gifs/dot_clr.gif"><BR>
<IMG align=top hspace=10 SRC="../cr_gifs/dot_clr.gif">
LNG must be stored in heavily insulated pressure vessels and provision must be made for &quot;boil-off&quot;, gas which has evaporated from the liquid form and will build up pressure in the vessel if not provided for. This can occur in both vehicles and storage facilities.<BR>
</td>
</tr>

<tr>
<td><A HREF="nichepg3.htm"><IMG align=left BORDER=0 SRC="../cr_gifs/back.gif"></A></td>
<td><br></td>
<td width=480>
<A HREF="nichepg5.htm"><IMG align=right BORDER=0 SRC="../cr_gifs/forward.gif"></A>
</td>
</tr>
</table>
<!-- end of table-->

<IMG align=top align=right vspace=1 SRC="../cr_gifs/dot_clr.gif"><br>
<IMG align=top align=left width=630 height=5 SRC="../cr_gifs/dot_catf.gif"><BR>
<IMG align=top align=right vspace=1 SRC="../cr_gifs/dot_clr.gif"><br>

<A HREF="../default.htm"><IMG BORDER=0 SRC="../cr_gifs/cr_home.gif" ALT="Review Homepage"></A>
