<DOCNO>WT04-B17-121</DOCNO>
<DOCOLDNO>IA006-000056-B016-29</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.bcr.bc.ca:80/catf/review/issue_27/afterpg2.htm 204.191.240.6 19970221185502 text/html 7566
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 21 Feb 1997 18:55:21 GMT
Server: WebSitePro/1.1g (S/N WPO-22E6)
Accept-ranges: bytes
Content-type: text/html
Last-modified: Mon, 17 Feb 1997 23:43:10 GMT
