<DOCOLDNO>IA006-000056-B016-425</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.bcr.bc.ca:80/catf/review/issue_20/ngvmark3.htm 204.191.240.6 19970221190147 text/html 7132
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 21 Feb 1997 19:02:08 GMT
Server: WebSitePro/1.1g (S/N WPO-22E6)
Accept-ranges: bytes
Content-type: text/html
Last-modified: Tue, 18 Feb 1997 00:45:54 GMT
