<DOCHDR>
http://www.bcr.bc.ca:80/catf/review/issue_22/ball_pg2.htm 204.191.240.6 19970221185736 text/html 6041
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Fri, 21 Feb 1997 18:57:55 GMT
