<p align=center><b><a name="appl">APPLICATION TECHNOLOGY</a></b></p>

<p>DEFINITION: This addresses the design and implementation of computer programs that solve user problems.  Its critical components are methodologies for understanding the needs and tasks of users; methodologies for designing applications and for development environments and for tool kits to build applications easily.</p>

