<p align=center><b><a name="stor">STORAGE</a></b></p>

<p>DEFINITION: Storage (optical & magnetic) includes magnetic and optical disks and tapes and their controllers for on-line backup and archival storage of data sets.  Together, these systems store the vast majority of all data stored in digital form.</p>

<p align=center>HIGH-IMPACT CRITICAL SUCCESS FACTORS:</p>
<ul>
<li>Capital Investment
<li>Critical Mass
<li>Large Market Size
