<p align=center><b><a name="manu">MANUFACTURING TECHNOLOGY</a></b></p>

<p>DEFINITION: This includes facilities, tools, information systems and infrastructures for manufacturing enterprise.  These systems are essential for cost-effective, high quality and responsive production processes for a wide range of computer systems and peripherals and their underlying technologies.  Elements of this technology include automated assembly, equipment and process tools; real-time planning and control systems; modeling and decision technologies and the underlying information systems that enable use of the technology.</p>

<p align=center>HIGH-IMPACT CRITICAL SUCCESS FACTORS:</p>
