<html>
<title>Goals and Benefits</title>
<h2>Goals and Benefits</h2>
<hr>

<p><b>GOAL: </b>Open APIs for emerging NII applications so applications will be able to run on a variety of NII platforms. </p>
 
 
<p><b>BENEFIT</b>: Open APIs for NII appliances, such as computers and set-top boxes, will allow users to choose from a wide variety of applications, and will ensure that such applications are compatible with those of users with different types of information appliances.  For example, software programmers will be able to write programs for interactive games to work with any information appliance, assuring users of a wide selection of applications regardless of the type of information appliance they purchase.</p>
<a href="report6.html">Return to the Main Report</a>
