<html>
<head><title>Figure 11</title>
<h2>Computer Equipment Market Share*</h2>
<hr>
<p>In spite of the U.S. computer industry's continuing heavy investment in R&D, the U.S. share of the world dcomputer systems market fell from about 60% to 40% between 1983 and 1989, while Japan's share rose from 8% to 22%, and Europe's share grew from 10% to 15%.</p>
<hr>
<img src="11.gif">
<hr>
<p>*Does not include software<br>Source:  International Trade Association</p>
</html>
