<h2>Alta Vista</h2>

<a href="http://www.altavista.digital.com/cgi-bin/query?pg=ah&what=web"> [ Help with Query]  </a>
</CENTER><CENTER><FORM method=GET action="http://www.altavista.digital.com/cgi-bin/query"><P><INPUT TYPE=hidden NAME=pg VALUE=aq>
<B> Search <SELECT NAME=what><OPTION VALUE=web SELECTED> the Web<OPTION VALUE=news > Usenet</SELECT>
  and Display the Results <SELECT NAME=fmt><OPTION VALUE="." SELECTED> in Standard Form<OPTION VALUE=c > in Compact Form<OPTION VALUE=d > in Detailed Form<OPTION VALUE=n > as a Count only</SELECT></B><BR>
<B> Selection Criteria: </B> Please use Advanced Syntax (AND, OR, NOT, and NEAR).<BR><textarea name=q cols=68 rows=3>
</textarea><p>
<B> Results Ranking Criteria: </B> Documents containing these words will be listed first.<BR><textarea name=r cols=68 rows=1></textarea><P> Start date	: <INPUT TYPE=text NAME=d0 SIZE=12 MAXLENGTH=32 VALUE="">  End date: <INPUT TYPE=text NAME=d1 SIZE=12 MAXLENGTH=32 VALUE=""> e.g. 21/Mar/96<BR><INPUT TYPE=submit VALUE=" Submit Advanced Query">
