<h1> Strathcourier </h1><p>
<h3>April - 1996</h3>
</center>
<P> This is an electronic version of the publication 'Strathcourier'.  Although many items are common to both, additions, alterations or deletions from the print version may be evident.<p>
<P> Welcome to the April edition of the Strathcourier.  The theme of this issue is 'Nurturing tall poppies..'<p>
Please choose from the following :<p>
<img src="icons/yello.gif"><a href="current.html">Realisation of Potential, Excellence and Achievement</a><p>
<img src="icons/yello.gif"><a href="career.html">Sowing the Seeds for Success</a><p>
If you would like additional information on any of the topics covered in this issue of 'Strathcourier' or would like a copy of this magazine please contact the school at:
Strathcona Baptist Girl's Grammar School<br>
34 Scott Street, Canterbury, Victoria, 3126 <br>
Telephone: 03 98361611   Fax: 03 98885440<p>
