<DT><H2><B>Australia Online</B></H2>
</DL>


<DT><H3>General Reference</H3>
<DD>The <A HREF = "http://www.aust.emb.nw.dc.us">Australian Embassy in Washington</A> offers a wide range of information about Australia.  Included are: the Economy, International Trade, Geography and Climate, Flora and  Fauna, People, History, Government and Culture.

<DD>The <A HREF = "http://tourism.gov.au">Federal Department of Tourism</A> offers a wide range of information about tourism in Australia.  This is a very good resource for finding information about Australia, tourist ventures and programs.
</DL>
