<DT><H3>News and Current Events</H3>
<DD>ABC TV's <A HREF = "http://www.ozemail.com.au:80/~btn/"> Behind The News </A> current events program.
<DD>International News Services</A>  This link includes pointer to all known international news services available on the Internet.<P>

<DD></IMG><A HREF = "http://www.ozemail.com.au:80/~btn/">Behind The News </A> ABC TV's popular current events program for students presents its World Wide Web service.  Available are details of upcoming programs, scripts from previous programs, hot topics and cool sites.<P>



<DD></IMG><A HREF = "http://bond.edu.au/gnn/gnn.html">GNN Network News</A>  This service offers information about the latest developments on the Internet along with some current events news.  You can find some interesting subjects offered on the GNN main menu.<P>
<DD></IMG><A HREF = "http://www.timeinc.com/time/universe.html">Time Magazine</A> The Time Magazine offers an up to date resource of articles and resources taken from Time, a Gateway to Internet resources and archives of other news media.  Information is offered under the following sections:Today's News, Time Magazine, Message Boards, Pathfinder,  Customer Service, Library, Internet Gateway and Offers and Information.  An excellent resource.<P>
