<TITLE>Strathcona - Employment </TITLE>

<body>
<BODY BACKGROUND="icons/back.gif" BGCOLOUR="#000000" VLINK="#8888ff" TEXT="#f5f50c" LINK="#ffffff" ALINK="#ff8888">


<h1>Employment and Carreer Information</h1></HEAD>

<LI><A TARGET="_top" HREF="http://www.yahoo.com/Regional/Countries/Australia/Employment/"><B>Yahoo - Australian Employment Opportunities. </A> Yahoo offers a comprehensive search facility for finding employment in a wide range of jobs, not only in Australia, but globally.</B> 
 <br>


<LI><A TARGET="_top" HREF="http://www.about-australia.com/employ.htm"><B>About Australia - Employment Opportunities</B></A><br>
Employment Opportunities in Australia.  Rainbow Office offer a fast, accurate Resume service for Local, National or International Job seekers.  This site contains a number of links to other employment agencies and information sources.<br>

<LI><A TARGET="_top" A href="http://www.jobnet.com.au/index.html>JobNet Australia</a><br>
JobNet is central index of Computer (IT) related employment opportunities in Australia, Asia and around the World. You can browse all the current job vacancies (updated daily) including skills specification and contact details including Email. (Search facilities available).<br>


<LI><A TARGET="_top" HREF="http://employment.com.au/index.html"><B>Employment Opportunities in Australia</B></A> <br>
 Covering a wide range of opportunities in many fields of emploment.<br>
<br>
</LI>
<LI><A TARGET="_top" HREF="http://www.deet.gov.au"><B>Department of Employment, Education, Training and Youth Affairs (Australia)</B></A> <br>


<LI><A TARGET="_top" HREF="http://137.154.148.24/stuff/jobs/index.html"><B>Employment Opportunities</B></A> <br>
Employment Opportunities -  The Australian Resume Server JobNet.  (Computer (IT) related employment opportunities in Australia). 

<LI><A TARGET="_top" HREF="http://minyos.xx.rmit.edu.au/~s9410536/empl.html"><B>Employment On-Line : DW InfoServer</B></A><br>
The Australian Resume Server.  Andersen Contracting is the second largest IT contracting firm in Asia/Pacific. Information Technology related contract employment in Australia, New Zealand, Hong Kong and more.

