<p><font color="#FFFFFF"></font>&nbsp;</p>
<p><font color="#FFFFFF">The Strathcona community embraces far more than present students, staff and Council.</font></p>
<p><font color="#FFFFFF">Proud of its history and traditions, its current students and of the women who are its graduates, the School acknowledges that 
its identity derives from all who have been involved in its past and who have contributed to its growth through their vision, 
work and financial support.</font></p>
<p><font color="#FFFFFF">The continued involvement of parents, Old Strathconians and friends is actively encouraged through support groups and 
through participation in all aspects of school life.</font></p>
<p><font color="#FFFFFF">We invite you to join our community. Please contact us for information on fees and scholarships,</font></p>
<p><font color="#FFFFFF">For an opportunity to find out how Strathcona can benefit your daughter, more information, or an appointment to visit, please 
contact the Registrar on (03) 9836 1611 or fill in the form below.</font></p>
