<html>

<head>
<title>Strong personal value</title>

</head>

<body>
<BODY BACKGROUND="icons/back.gif" BGCOLOUR="#000000" VLINK="#8888ff" TEXT="#f5f50c" LINK="#ffffff" ALINK="#ff8888">
<img src="icons/values.gif">
<B><I><center><font color="#FFFF00"><em>Strathcona develops girls and gives them the motivation to achieve their goals with courage 
and commitment.</em></font></B></i></center><body>

<h3><font color="#FFFF00">The Foundations of our Success</font></h3>
<p><font color="#FFFFFF">At Strathcona, we place absolute importance on the uniqueness and worth of each person. It is this focus which many believe 
to be the single most important characteristic of a Strathcona education. </font></p>
<p><font color="#FFFFFF">Pastoral Care is integral to creating a learning environment in which individuals feel happiest and most comfortable. Our 
program, both innovative and comprehensive, builds self-esteem and assurance, develops leadership skills and encourages 
commitment to service in the wider community.</font></p>
<p><font color="#FFFFFF">Strathcona challenges young people to develop strong personal values. Girls are encouraged to develop responsibility and to 
explore individual conscience through an understanding of the Christian faith, together with the promotion of respect for one 
another and for different cultures and beliefs.</font></p>
<p><font color="#FFFFFF">Open communication and understanding between students and teachers are vital to the establishment and maintenance of a 
successful learning environment. Regular contact between the chaplain, counsellors and pastoral teachers fosters 
understanding and concern for each individual. This ensures that support is given whenever there is a need, and strengthens the 
culture that sets Strathcona apart.</font></p>
<p><font color="#FFFFFF">Visitors to the School frequently comment on the happy atmosphere. Interaction between students is promoted through 
programs such as &quot;Big Sister Little Sister&quot; which matches girls from the Junior School with older girls. Such programs assist 
further in building rapport between students of different levels and cultivating a sense of care and concern for others.</font></p>
<p><font color="#FFFFFF">Strathcona's close-knit community and caring, supportive staff help girls to become assured, thoughtful young women, with an 
intelligent awareness of the world and an appreciation of their part in it.</font></p>
<h3><font color="#FFFF00">An Educational Environment in which to Thrive</font></h3>
<p><font color="#FFFFFF">Extensive facilities, covering more than 5 hectares over two campuses, offer girls a superb opportunity for personal growth 
and development. They allow us to provide a diverse range of cultural, sporting, vocational and outdoor activities.</font></p>
<p>&#160;</p>
<p>&#160;</p>


<center>
<P>
