<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<p align=center><a href="./susanvil.wrl"><img src="./graphics/susanvil.gif" align=bottom border=0 width=450 height=143></a> </p>
<p align=center>You are the <img src="http://www.scruznet.com/cgi-bin/counter?ft=0|frgb=0;0;0|tr=0|trgb=0;0;0|wxh=15;20|md=6|dd=B|df=cannon4528.dat" align=bottom> vistor since February 2, 1997. Welcome! </p>
<p align=center><a href="./outdoors/index.html"><b>Outdoors:</b></a> <i>Outdoor experiences and resources</i> </p>
<p align=center><a href="./home-n-garden/index.html"><b>Home &amp; Garden:</b></a> <i>Home crafts, recipes and gardens.</i> </p>
<p align=center><img src="./graphics/stest.gif" align=bottom width=54 height=54></p>
<table width=100%>
<tr><td width=50%><p align=center><strong>What's New</strong> </p>
</td><td width=50%><p align=center><strong>About Susanville.com &amp; Virtual Susanville</strong> </p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td width=50%><p>Alford has taught at <a href="/home-n-garden/food/classes">Draegers</a> several times - one 
such time he prepared &quot;Yogurt and Pomegranate 
Dip&quot;; he served it with fresh warm flatbread. The 
flavor and textures were ah inspiring. The recipe is on 
page 193 in <a href="http://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ISBN=0-688-11411-3/susanvillecomA/">Flatbreads &amp; Flavor</a> by Jeffery Alford 
and Naomi Duguid.</p>
<p align=center> <img src="home-n-garden/food/cookbooks/flatbred.gif" align=bottom width=108 height=133> </p>
</td><td width=50%><a href="about.html">Susanville.com</a> is a small cyber community where you 
can find a collage of information for enjoying the 
Western United States today.   <p>Click <a href="howto.html">here</a> to learn more about Virtual Susanville & VRML.</p><p>Although this site has tidbits of <a href="./history.html">history</a> on the 
<a href="http://maps.yahoo.com/yt.hm?FAM=yahoo&amp;CMD=GEO&amp;SEC=geo&amp;AD2=&amp;AD3=Susanville">Susanville, California</a>, this site does not represent the 
town. For present day information you must call the 
Chamber of Commerce (916) 257-4323. </p>
</td></tr>
</table>
