<head>
<title>About Susanville.com</title>

</head>

<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
<h1 align=center>About Susanville.com</h1>
<p>California's pioneer history is richly steeped in adventure and invention. Virtual Susanville of a 
collection of all the life sustaining resources needed to thrive today as the Internet experiences its 
own Gold Rush.  Susanville, California in Northeastern California that flurished in the time of the Gold Rush.</p>
<p>This web site in no way attempts to be an 'official' representative for the physical town of 
Susanville. </p>
<p align=center><a href="http://www.susanville.com"><img src="./graphics/stest.gif" border=0 align=bottom width=54 height=54></a></p>
</body>

