<h1 align=center><tt>AMI NEWSLETTER</tt></h1>
<p align=center><strong><tt>The Alliance for the Mentally Ill of Santa Clara County</tt></strong></p>
<table width=100%>
<tr><td width=50%><pre><strong><tt>February  1997</tt></strong> </pre>
</td><td width=50%><div align=right>
<pre><strong><tt>Volume XXV No. 2</tt></strong> </pre>
