<h1 align=center><tt>AMI NEWSLETTER</tt></h1>
<p align=center><strong><tt>The Alliance for the Mentally Ill of Santa Clara County</tt></strong></p>
<table width=100%>
<tr>
<td width=50%><pre><strong><tt>September 1996</tt></strong></pre></td>
<td width=50%><div align=right><pre><strong><tt>Volume XXII No. 9</tt></strong></pre></div></td>
