<p>
<tt>The dinner will be held Friday in her honor after twenty seven and a half years of dedicated County service.  It will start at 6:00 PM, for no host cocktails, with Dinner at 7:PM.  Lou's Village is at 1465 West San Carlos (on the right hand side a half block west of North Meridian).  RSVP to Maria Rivera, Older Adult Division, 645 South Bascom Ave., San Jose, CA 95128 or Phone 408.885.7590.  Cost for complete dinner is $32 with choice of vegetarian pasta, chicken or beef.  RSVP deadline is Tuesday, September 3.  Please make checks to Jo Gampon.</tt>
</p>
