<h2 align=center><tt>Supplies</tt></h2>
<table width=100%>
<tr><td width=30%><img src="fibretech.gif" align=bottom width=204 height=144></td><td width=50%><strong>Set of Three</strong> <em>(small, medium, large)</em> <strong>$10.00</strong><p><strong>The Wooden Cable Needle</strong></p>
<p>These needles are made in the USA of a natural finish wood 
(maple or birch). The more you use them, the more 
&quot;conditioned&quot; they will become! The natural oils from wool, and 
also from your skin, will help create a soft finish over time. 
Keep them behind your ear (like a pencil) between cable twists 
to help the finish even more. </p>
</td></tr>

