<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" text="#000000">

<h2 align="center"><a href="index.html"><img
src="images/cmlogot.gif" alt="Copper Mountain Financial Group"
border="0" width="652" height="74"></a></h2>

<p><br>
</p>

<h3>Copper Mountain Financial Group Profile</h3>

<p><img src="images/pookline.gif" width="722" height="13"> </p>

<p>The Copper Mountain Financial Group is one of the West's
leading providers of trust and investment advisory
services--specializing in the management of retirement assets. </p>

<p>The company's primary clients are corporate pension and 401(k)
retirement plans (and their participants), institutional
investors, and high-net worth individuals. </p>

<p>The firm offers professional administrative, custodial and
regulatory compliance services to trust accounts, retirement
plans, and IRAs, as well as a full service investment advisory
group representing the nation's leading money management
professionals. </p>

<p>The mission of the Copper Mountain Financial Group is to guide
and advise our clients of successful ways to invest in their
future. We do so by providing the services and support necessary
to help companies and their employees invest and manage their
retirement asset in a disciplined fashion--optimally leading to
well-funded retirement plans. </p>

<table border="0" cellpadding="10">
    <tr>
        <td valign="top"><em><strong>Total Assets:</strong></em></td>
        <td>$4.1 Billion</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td valign="top"><em><strong>Assets Under Management:</strong></em></td>
        <td>$905 Million</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td valign="top"><em><strong>Geographic Area of Coverage:</strong></em></td>
        <td>The Pacific Northwest including:<br>
        Oregon, Washington, and Idaho. <p>Northern California and
        Alaska.</p>
        </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td valign="top"><em><strong>Representative Clients:</strong></em></td>
