<title>Copper Mountain Financial Group - Sub-Advisors</title>
</head>

<body bgcolor="#FFFFFF" text="#000000">

<h2 align="center"><a href="index.html"><img
src="images/cmlogot.gif" alt="Copper Mountain Financial Group"
border="0" width="652" height="74"></a></h2>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<h3>Profiles of our Sub-Advisors.</h3>

<p><img src="images/pookline.gif" width="722" height="13"> </p>

<p>Copper Mountain Financial Group selects and monitors
excellent, proven national money management companies, reflecting
a broad spectrum of investment philosophies. It then works
closely with clients to identifty their specific investment goals
and policies surrounding their retirement plans and works
collaboratively to select those specific managers whose styles
will be employed to achieve the chosen goals. </p>

<p>Next, Copper Mountain Financial Group carefully monitors
ongoing investment performance and reports to its clients how the
selected money management team is performing against market
indices and established goals. Periodic reviews confirm either
that the chosen path is succeeding and that it should be
continued or that fine-tuning is needed and necessary amendments
are made. </p>

<p>The following are the current sub-advisors selected by Copper
Mountain Financial: </p>

<table border="0" cellpadding="2">
    <tr>
        <td><strong>Subadvisor</strong></td>
        <td><strong>Style</strong></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td><a href="cohen.htm">Cohen, Klingenstein &amp; Marks</a></td>
        <td>Large Cap Growth</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td><a href="equinox.htm">Equinox Capital Management</a></td>
        <td>Large Cap Value</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td><a href="gam.htm">Global Asset Management, Inc.</a></td>
        <td>International</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td><a href="kopp.htm">Kopp Investment Advisors</a></td>
        <td>Emerging Growth</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td><a href="morley.htm">Morley Capital Management, Inc.</a></td>
        <td>Stable Asset</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td><a href="pimco.htm">Pacific Investment Management
        Company</a></td>
        <td>Fixed Income</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td><a href="progress.htm">Progressive Securities
        Financial Services Corporation </a></td>
        <td>Socially Responsible</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
