<h2 align="center"><a href="index.html"><img
src="images/cmlogot.gif" alt="Copper Mountain Financial Group"
border="0" width="652" height="74"></a></h2>

<p><br>
</p>

<h3>Master Custody and Trustee Services</h3>

<p><img src="images/pookline.gif" width="722" height="13"> </p>

<p>Copper Mountain Trust Corporation, a wholly owned subsidiary
of the Copper Mountain Financial Group, has grown from an asset
base of only $119 million to over $4 billion in eight years
because it provides the very highest quality custody, trustee and
administrative services available in the Northwest. Copper
Mountain Trust Corporation is a boutique and we are in this
business to stay. We feel strongly that the decision to employ a
particular master custodian/trustee should be based upon the
custodians commitment to service, depth and experience,
responsiveness, and innovation. </p>

<p>Copper Mountain is known for: </p>

<ul>
    <li><em><strong>Focus</strong></em><strong>.</strong>
        Providing trustee and custody services for all types of
        retirement plans is our only business. We are not forced
        to contend with sharp cuts in manpower and budgets
        because of poor decisions made elsewhere in the
        organization&#151;an inherent problem with our bank
        competition. All our capital and human resource talent is
        focused on providing the best available service. </li>
    <li><em><strong>Depth and Experience</strong></em>. Our
        administrative team has over 70 years of combined ERISA
        and Taft-Hartley experience, including years in
        Washington, DC working with the IRS and DOL on retirement
        plan issues. Operationally, our systems are state-of-the-art.
        Our ability to handle complex transactions is equal or
        superior to our competition. </li>
    <li><em><strong>Flexibility</strong></em>. We conform to the
        needs of our clients. For instance, should you require a
        special report prepared, or a wire sent in one day, you
        will find us responsive and the need taken care of
        quickly. </li>
    <li><em><strong>Innovative and Proactive</strong></em>. Our
        work on the establishment of strategic relationships
        which bring our clients world class services, such as the
        Bank of New York Security Lending Program, is an example
        of the creative ways we assist our clients. We use advanced
        information technology, including the Internet, to
        provide a high level of service. </li>
</ul>

<p>It is interesting to note what has happened to custody
services within the banking community. The October 18, 1993 issue
of Pension and Investments quotes Michael Costa, principal of
master trust consultants, MLC Associates, </p>

<blockquote>
    <p>&#147;There&#146;s been a general decline in the quality
    of administrative services provided to sponsors in the market
    and clients are perceiving it.&#148;</p>
</blockquote>

<p>The article further states that Mr. Costa...</p>

<blockquote>
    <p>&#147;...has helped sponsors in a number of searches for
    new custodians this year. Many decided to retain their
    present service provider not because they really like the
    service they&#146;re getting, but after looking at the market
    they don&#146;t see anything much better.&#148;</p>
</blockquote>

<p>Fed up with the decline of your Banks service level? Going
through another Bank merger? Things are different at Copper
Mountain. Copper Mountain Trust Corporation is committed to the
master custody and trustee business. It is our only business. All
our capital and human resource talent is focused on providing the
best available service. We must and do excel. </p>

<p><img src="images/pookline.gif" width="722" height="13"> </p>

<table border="0" cellpadding="5">
    <tr>
        <td><a href="mailto:info@copper-mt.com "><img
        src="images/mailbox.gif" alt="Contact Copper Mountain"
        align="middle" border="0" width="35" height="35"></a> </td>
        <td>For more information, contact Copper Mountain
        marketing and sales at: <br>
        <a href="   mailto:info@copper-mt.com">info@copper-mt.com</a> </td>
    </tr>
