<p><a href="navs.htm">Current Daily NAV's</a></p>

<h3>IMPORTANT NOTES:</h3>

<p>(1) Performance on all funds in existance as of January 1,
1996. </p>

<p>Performance data quoted on the commingled trust funds is
historical and includes changes in unit/share price and
reinvestment of dividends and capital gains (if any). Data quoted
represents past performance and does not guarantee future
results. Future returns and principal value may fluctuate so that
an investor's units/shares, when redeemed, may be worth more or
less than the original cost. No investment in any of the funds is
insured or guaranteed by the U.S. Government including the FDIC.
Ownership of these commingled trust funds is limited to
tax-exempt retirement accounts of Copper Mountain Trust
Corporation. </p>

<p>Because account fees can vary, performance of the commingled
funds does not reflect management fees and expenses that are paid directly
by accounts invested in the Fund. The Stable Asset, Fixed Income,
Money Market, International, and S&amp;P 500 Funds have invested,
at the discretion of the advisor (Copper Mountain Trust
Corporation), in other commingled trust or mutual funds that have
the same investment objective as commingled trust fund. During
periods that Copper Mountain's commingled trust fund invests in
other funds, the performance data shown represents the
performance of the underlying funds and reflects all fees and
expenses of that fund. </p>

