<h3 align="center">Through its single-minded pursuit of building
wealth for each client, Copper Mountain is the Northwest's
pre-eminent independent investment services company.</h3>

<p align="center">New or updated information as of December 11,
1996, but NAV information is <img src="images/updated.gif"
alt="Updated" width="56" height="8"> daily. </p>

<p align="center"><img src="images/pookline.gif" width="722"
