<h3><font size="4"><strong>Retirement Calculator - Disclosure
Statement</strong></font></h3>

<p><img src="images/pookline.gif" width="722" height="13"></p>

<p>&nbsp;</p>

<p>This retirement calculator is intended to serve as an
educational tool, not investment advice. Your circumstances are
unique; therefore, you need to assess your own situation and
consult an investment professional if you feel you need more
personal advice. Also, your circumstances will probably change
over time, so review your financial strategy periodically to be
sure it continues to fit your situation. All examples are
hypothetical and are intended for illustrative purposes only.<font
color="#000000" size="2"> This calculator assumes investments are
made into a tax-deferred retirement account.</font></p>

