<p>
technology has been good to men, providing designers with stretchy new fabrics to get the fit just (ugggh) right and to produce visual effects once available only to the imagination.
<p>
<a href="brief2.html">
<img src="brief2_sm.jpg" width=99 height=161
align=right vspace=0 border=0 hspace=0 alt=""></a>
