<p>
<a href="blinds.html">
<img src="blinds_sm.jpg" width=235 height=155
align=left vspace=3 border=0 hspace=0 alt=""></a>
the underwear fetish is upon us again  but its always been nearby, celebrated throughout the ages in sculpture, photography, movies, illustration and in the current explosion of mens understuff that has grown into a five billion dollar industry.
<p>
from tom cruise dancing in his briefs in risky business to marky mark, snug in his calvins, the underwear fetish is a special flavor of male eroticism.</td>
