but coleys adventures are perhaps the deepest, richest, storytelling in the comix world thanks to their complex characters and situations. the pages are beautifully crafted and blackburns illustration is unique. it is erotic comix art from a thoughtful artist and writer who challenges his hero, and our perceptions of sexuality, with his pen.</td>
</TABLE>

