<TD VALIGN=top WIDTH=250 ALIGN=left>
<font face="arial, helvetica" size=2><b>
<a href="teddy1.html">
<img src="teddy1_sm.jpg" width=125 height=239
align=right vspace=0 hspace=9 border=0></a>teddy of paris was born in marseille in 1961 of corsican and sicilian blood, a passionate brew. he has lived in paris half his life, studied french and art history at the sarbonne, but teddy of paris has never taken an art class. 
<p>
his classical influences include michangelo, tintoreto and caravaggio. among his heroes of today are tom of finland, etienne, brad parker and the hun. his stippled work draws from the techniques of new yorks rex. 

<a href="teddy3.html">
<img src="teddy3_sm.jpg" width=100 height=216 align=right vspace=3 hspace=9 border=0 alt=""></a>
you can see the effects of all these artists on teddys stuff, but he adds his own brand of high-octane sexuality.
<p>

teddys work is widely seen in europe. some of his best crotch stuff is here, though hes also adept at hardcore scenes. teddy has been published extensively in <u>gai pied hebdo</u>, <u>s magazine</u>, <u>rebell</u>, <u>exit le journal</u>, <u>dialogai</u>, <u>stroke</u> and <u>manifest reader</u>.</b></td>
